---
description: General project conventions for Portfolio Kayro Gomes
globs: ["**/*"]
---
- React 18 + TypeScript + Vite + Tailwind CSS v4 + React Router 7
- Content centralized in `src/app/data/site.ts` and `src/app/data/projects.ts`
- All user-facing text in PT-BR
- Use Tailwind utility classes, no inline styles (except ScrollZoomImage dynamic transforms)
- No `cn()` or shadcn/ui utilities — they were removed
- Conventional Commits enforced by commitlint
- Tests: Vitest + React Testing Library, colocated `*.test.ts(x)` files
- Lint: ESLint 9 + simple-import-sort + react-hooks
- Format: Prettier (single quotes, 100 char width)